    Notification Component

    Context:
    * message - Notification message (required)
    * type - Notification type: success, error, warning, info (default: info)
    * dismissible - Can be dismissed (boolean)

    Example:
    {{> core/notification }}
}}
<div class="notification notification-{{type}}{{#dismissible}} dismissible{{/dismissible}}" role="alert">
    {{#dismissible}}
    <button type="button" class="notification-close" aria-label="{{#str}}close{{/str}}">
        Ã—
    </button>
    {{/dismissible}}
    <div class="notification-content">
        {{{message}}}
    </div>
</div>
